and have peace of mind. Boy, can I ever relate to having a bunch of bags cluttering my space all the time!

over the green egg far and away. The green egg can wait so I will get that list to you before noon,

I know you will be busy with work today, and it’s a Monday . So I promise not to be unrealistic about response times here, So I will just do my best if
you’re not able to get back to me. There’s nothing life or death going on here that we can’t just course correct.
Please do let me know how Adrian is doing. He sounded really bad yesterday. I hope you have a wonderful day and we are productive as a team. Please
let me know if there’s anything at all I can do for you and I will do my best to make it happen.
Best
robert
